node.text: From reefs to ridges, explore the beauty of the Philippines through the eyes of the locals. While 2020 has been a year of change for travel, the Philippines is excited to invite local visitors to explore the beautiful islands. The #BDTeam had the pleasure of working with @tourism_phl to highlight beautiful places around the Philippines. The opportunities for exploration are endless-from the Hundred Island National Park in Pangasinan to exploring the Suba and Culili Sand Dunes in Ilocos Norte.

node.text:
With an incredibly rich history, being an “Egyptian” can have many facets especially when it comes to creativity. Today, we’re sharing a unique story dedicated to any creative who intends to carve their own path no matter the circumstances. 

“It’s proof that the end product most of the time doesn’t pan out the way you expect it. And its by having expectations that you hinder your potential.” - @matiasderada

Watch this beautiful film on Beautiful Destinations Youtube channel. 🇪🇬

🎥 @matiasderada #BDTeam

Bristol Bay, one of Alaska’s most treasured natural wonders, is under threat. @world_wildlife 

It’s home to an irreplaceable ecosystem and one of the last salmon strongholds. Not only that, its iconic wildlife has sprung up a sustainable tourism industry which effects thousands of Alaskan livelihoods.

All of this is under threat if the Pebble Mine moves forward. The recent approval of the environmental impact statement has made it clear that our voices need to be heard. 

Nature and people can’t live without fresh water, and Bristol Bay is the lifeblood that sustains every species calling the region home. 

On a recent trip to Alaska, the #BDTeam and WWF Ambassador, @jeremyjauncey, learned firsthand about the conservation community’s fight against Pebble Mine.

node.text: As New York City starts to open back up, we wanted to take a moment to reflect on the efforts of heroes in the hospitality industry who have been helping our frontline workers. @fsnewyork was the first hotel in New York City to open its door to our frontline workers and provide them with a safe haven to stay during such an uncertain time. They quickly transformed the hotel into a near medical-grade facility. Over 300 medical workers called @fsnewyork home during this time as they were provided rooms free of charge. This allowed them to keep their own families safe as they focused on their work and taking care of patients. ❤️ (🎥: @loganlambert 📸: @loganstrongarms 📍: Four Seasons Hotel New York)

node.text:
Catching some noodles with @kotravellers in Hirobun, a laid-back riverside restaurant in Kyoto’s Kurama and Kibune district. If you're up for a gastronomic Japan trip, bookmark this! 😋🍜

"What you see here is Nagashi Somen, which is a special way of serving thin white noodles. The noodles travel down a sliced bamboo pipe with flowing cold water. You then have to catch the noodles with chopsticks before they pass by you or are snatched up by someone else. There is also a cold dipping sauce that you dunk them in before eating (as seen performed immaculately by Kate). Lastly, when the red noodles come out it means your time is over."

If you’re worrying about hygiene, don’t fret! The bamboo is changed every batch, the leftover noodles will not be recycled, and the staff assigns one flume per group—which means you will only be sharing your flume among your company. 🎋❤️

Who else wants to try this in Japan? 🇯🇵

📽 @kotravellers 
📍 Kyoto, Japan
🎶 Yoshida Brothers - Fukaki Umi No Kanata (Beyond the Deep Sea)

Is this your kind of place or do you prefer the bustle of the city? 🍃

Edward Scissorhands' doing spotted by @brigrc. 🌳 This fabulous tree was shot in Lenno, a charming small town on the shores of Lake Como that's one of Italy's best-kept secrets. 😍

Tucked on the west shore of Lake Como, Lenno is a less crowded place than other villages surrounding the lake but is no less beautiful. When in Lenno, you must visit Villa del Balbianello, one of the popular villas on the lake that's known for its stunning gardens. Whether you're here for a day trip or a longer stay, your trip will surely be a memorable one. 🍃

Taking a breath of fresh air with @ellchintya in this invigorating corner nestled in Bali. Besides lush rice fields, mesmerizing beaches, and hip locales, the Indonesian province also features stunning waterfalls that provide a fresh escape. 💦

The Banyu Wana Amertha Waterfall is home to four stunning and diverse waterfalls that are each worth visiting. If you plan to explore this place, allot a couple of hours so you can take a dip and immerse in the verdant surroundings. 🍃

The best way to get here is to rent a scooter or hire a private car and driver, which you can book online. The travel time is about a 60-90 minute drive from Ubud. 📝

Did you know this place existed in Bali? 🇮🇩

📽 @ellchintya 
📍 Banyu Wana Amertha Waterfall, Bali, Indonesia
🎶 Waterfalls - TLC

This seaside corner in Portofino via @lumadeline is currently the summer setting we're all daydreaming about. ☀️ A paradise by the sea, Portofino is an exquisite town where sailing, diving, hiking, and exploring the coastline are favorite pastimes. Its tranquil harbor is home to sailboats and luxury vessels, while its shore is awash with quaint fisherman houses, laid-back cafés, and stylish bars. A sunny escape here will surely enthrall even the most discerning travelers! 🇮🇹

What are your favorite summer destinations and why?

Paragliding pilot @marcellauchoa shows us her unbelievable view taken during the Paragliding World Cup 2021 in Kopaonik, Serbia. 🤩

Whether you want to know how it feels like to fly, or if you want to enjoy Kopaonik's lush landscapes from a bird's eye perspective, paragliding is the way to go! All throughout the year, the mountain range offers ideal locations with suitable conditions from where paragliders can take off and fly. Whether you're a beginner or an export, you'll surely enjoy paragliding here. 🪂

Is paragliding a sport you ever thought of trying? 🙌🏼

📽 @marcellauchoa
📍 Kopaonik, Serbia 
🎶 SHAED - Trampoline (Jauz Remix)

The Glarnerland views of @syifa_in_switzerland are making us dream of a relaxing and nature-filled Switzerland getaway. 😌

Though not as popular as its other counterparts, Glanerland is a gem that you won't regret visiting. Whether you're looking for picturesque hiking paths, scenic biking trails, or fun family excursions, Glanerland has so much to offer, especially for those seeking a beautiful and down-to-earth vacation. 🇨🇭

Have you ever heard of this incredible destination? 🌿
